```plantuml
@startuml xydo1990_mlops_zoomcamp_homework

actor Developer
actor User

participant "Jupyter Notebook" as Jupyter
participant "Data Script" as GetData
participant "Model Training Script" as TrainModel
participant "MLflow" as MLflow
participant "Docker" as Docker
participant "Prefect" as Prefect
participant "Batch Prediction Service" as BatchService
participant "Streaming Prediction Service" as StreamService
participant "Evidently" as Evidently
participant "Test Suite" as TestSuite

Developer -> Jupyter: Explore Data
Jupyter -> GetData: Load Data from Kaggle
GetData -> Jupyter: Data Loaded
Developer -> TrainModel: Train Model
TrainModel -> GetData: Download Data
GetData -> TrainModel: Data Ready
TrainModel -> MLflow: Log Experiment
MLflow -> TrainModel: Log Complete
Developer -> MLflow: Register Model
MLflow -> Docker: Deploy Model
Docker -> BatchService: Create Batch Container
Docker -> StreamService: Create Stream Container
Prefect -> BatchService: Schedule Batch Predictions
User -> StreamService: Send Stream Data
StreamService -> User: Return Predictions
Evidently -> BatchService: Monitor Batch Predictions
Evidently -> StreamService: Monitor Stream Predictions
TestSuite -> BatchService: Run Integration Tests
TestSuite -> StreamService: Run Integration Tests

@enduml
```